{"tid":2262541,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"17歲少年被指去年11月11日黃大仙堵路 罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-10-29T07:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T08:56:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1dda693eefcb7689633f571a58a1509e0eb5e343","tid":2262541,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10782&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KisemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=97f34896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10782</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#葉啟亮裁判官<br />\n#1111黃大仙<br />\n#裁決<br />\n<br />\n速報<br />\n<br />\n張 (17)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n在公眾地方造成阻礙<br />\n<br />\n❌罪名不成立❌<br />\n<br />\n詳情後補"},{"pid":"6958d9bcd1cd762acd4178ab780cf6ec37a63415","tid":2262541,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb66e5a2b51b5d6084485af9d96e1605588810d6","tid":2262541,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9a2a551b0a6841608d082ddf79bcd96b054371","tid":2262541,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb66e5a2b51b5d6084485af9d96e1605588810d6","tid":2262541,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b7657024c5f5605c3083dfaf07eb982066492d","tid":2262541,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"而家根本得果幾隻狗官瘋狂尻判"},{"pid":"2d18d2ac85e162a640578342931e0f85c0b285b8","tid":2262541,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e27a5bdbd761ceaf578c4025351d64c86adebf8","tid":2262541,"uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">去年11月11日有網民發起「全港大三罷」，有示威者在黃大仙對開堵路，期間一名中學生被指參與其中，被控一項在公眾地方造成阻礙。男生否認控罪，案件今（29日）在九龍城法院裁決。裁判官葉啓亮指，案發現場是行人路，而警方在被告身上又沒搜到任何可疑物品，認為沒有足夠證據證明他曾參與集結或堵路，遂裁定他罪名不成立。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n控方案情指，當日早上9時許，有警車巡經現場時，見到沙田坳道對開有約50人聚集，有人大叫口號，也有人取來雜物堵路。警員落車驅散，期間見到被告逃跑，途中又將背囊掉到地上，遂將他截停。<br />\n<br />\n辯方案情則指，被告到黃大仙站才知車站關閉，當時他在街上瀏覽交通情況，見防暴警迎面而來，感到害怕於是逃跑，途中覺得背囊累贅所以掉低，強調他沒有參與集結。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">裁判官裁決時指，沒有證供顯示被告當時手持可疑物件，而警員無論在他身上或背囊中，亦沒有檢獲任何可疑物品。此外，涉案地點是在行人路上，有不少街坊在場，單靠被告身穿黑衫黑褲，根本不足以證明被告曾參與堵路。再者，就被告被發現時的地點，警員的補錄口供與庭上繪畫的草圖並不一致，其證供準確性存疑，故裁定被告無罪。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d152b76e3118c3323f1439e69c6a1b2277270fc9","tid":2262541,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"葉啟亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700284df2431851992266b8e1ffdf07dbb2fe3e8","tid":2262541,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"鳩拉鳩告 香港人埋單"},{"pid":"bfc0141229762e0926162736984b70e518826dba","tid":2262541,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62b7657024c5f5605c3083dfaf07eb982066492d","tid":2262541,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"而家根本得果幾隻狗官瘋狂尻判"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:56:20.000Z","msg":"鄭門二傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> +蘇文膿"},{"pid":"f68dbfdb2914458314dc2baba4a465f2edad2026","tid":2262541,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"Dojoke 準備上訴未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab13db4c8c27ab2fb85924d2fc911b0266673a1a","tid":2262541,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7125cc91834eee4a3a0854feb41293939720a10f","tid":2262541,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:33:46.000Z","msg":"張聞判後接受傳媒訪問，坦言現時鬆一口氣，呼籲市民不要忘記其他示威者，希望人們前來旁聽聲援。"},{"pid":"40be46f85342c38464f7a10da542801cbaab341b","tid":2262541,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d152b76e3118c3323f1439e69c6a1b2277270fc9","tid":2262541,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"葉啟亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fa1044125b4b5efe54413cfb2feec3ee937cab","tid":2262541,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40be46f85342c38464f7a10da542801cbaab341b","tid":2262541,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d152b76e3118c3323f1439e69c6a1b2277270fc9","tid":2262541,"ui